query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, up.permission_id 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN user_permissions up ON u.id = up.user_id 
WHERE u.name LIKE '%غادة%' OR u.name LIKE '%سماح%'
ORDER BY u.name, up.permission_id;
